detail_description: Join the LEGO City Coast Guard and patrol the waters with this exciting Water Car set. The Water Car features a powerful motor and realistic design. Help the Coast Guard officer save the day and keep the waters safe!
Join the LEGO City Fire Brigade and save the day! This Fire Station set includes a fire truck, helicopter, and firefighter minifigures. Be prepared for exciting firefighting adventures!

toy_name: LEGO City Arctic Mobile Exploration Base
detail_description: Embark on an arctic expedition with the LEGO City Arctic Mobile Exploration Base! This set features a mobile lab, snowmobiles, and explorer minifigures. Discover hidden treasures in the icy wilderness!

Join the LEGO City Police force and maintain law and order! This Police Station set features a police station building, police car, helicopter, and minifigures of police officers. Solve crimes and keep the city safe!
All aboard the LEGO City Passenger Train! This set includes a motorized train, platform, and passenger cars. Pick up and drop off passengers for a fun railway adventure!

toy_name: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes Avengers Tower Battle
detail_description: Join the epic battle with the Avengers at the iconic Avengers Tower! Defend the tower from the evil Thanos and his minions. Features multiple floors, a rotating turret, and minifigures of your favorite superheroes.

toy_name: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes Iron Man Hall of Armor
detail_description: Enter Tony Stark's high-tech workshop with the LEGO Iron Man Hall of Armor! This set includes minifigures of Iron Man, Pepper Potts, and more. Suit up and join the battle against villains!

toy_name: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes Spider-Man: Far From Home Stark Jet and the Drone Attack
detail_description: Team up with Spider-Man and Nick Fury to stop the drone attack! This set includes the Stark Jet and minifigures of Spider-Man, Mysterio, and Nick Fury. Protect the world from the sinister threats!

toy_name: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes Thanos: Ultimate Battle
detail_description: Prepare for an epic showdown with Thanos! This set features the Guardians' Ship, Iron Man, Star-Lord, Gamora, and Thanos minifigures. Join the battle to save the universe!

toy_name: LEGO Marvel Super Heroes The Hulkbuster: Ultron Edition
detail_description: Unleash the power of the Hulkbuster with this Ultron Edition set! This highly detailed set includes a Hulkbuster figure and minifigures of Bruce Banner, Falcon, and Proxima Midnight. Engage in epic battles and protect humanity!

Recreate epic battles from Star Wars with the LEGO AT-AT Walker. This iconic vehicle features posable legs, a rotating turret, and minifigures of Luke Skywalker, General Veers, and AT-AT Driver. Prepare for intergalactic adventures!
Join the adventures in the iconic Millennium Falcon! This massive set includes minifigures of Han Solo, Chewbacca, Leia Organa, and more. Build and display this legendary starship!
Recreate the iconic Death Star battle scene! This set includes multiple rooms, minifigures of Darth Vader, Luke Skywalker, and more. Join the Rebel Alliance and save the galaxy!

Join the Rebel Alliance and pilot the iconic X-wing Starfighter! This set features a detailed starfighter, cockpit, and minifigures of Luke Skywalker and R2-D2. Engage in thrilling space battles against the Empire!

toy_name: LEGO Star Wars Imperial Star Destroyer
detail_description: Command the mighty Imperial Star Destroyer and rule the galaxy! This massive set includes minifigures of Darth Vader, Imperial Officer, and more. Build and display the symbol of the Empire!

toy_name: LEGO Speed Champions Porsche 911 GT3 RS
detail_description: Experience the power and speed of the Porsche 911 GT3 RS! This set features a detailed model, adjustable rear spoiler, and a minifigure of a race car driver. Take it to the racetrack and conquer the competition!

toy_name: LEGO Speed Champions Ferrari F8 Tributo
detail_description: Drive the iconic Ferrari F8 Tributo on the racetrack! This set includes a buildable Ferrari, race car driver minifigure, and a trophy. Experience the thrill of speed and victory!

toy_name: LEGO Speed Champions Lamborghini Urus ST-X & Lamborghini Huracán Super Trofeo EVO
detail_description: Get ready for a thrilling race with the Lamborghini Urus ST-X and Huracán Super Trofeo EVO! This set features two buildable Lamborghini cars, a start line, and race car driver minifigures. Speed towards victory in style!
